50:39.729 --> 50:41.314
Who the fuck are you guys?

50:42.523 --> 50:44.066
- Huh?
- ♪ (TENSE MUSIC PLAYS) ♪

50:44.066 --> 50:46.527
Come on, come on,
come on, come on. Let's go!

50:47.570 --> 50:49.530
Hurry up!

50:49.530 --> 50:52.492
Just keep moving.
Easy for you to say.

50:52.492 --> 50:54.869
Now you know how that stupid CIA
gait-alterer felt.

50:54.869 --> 50:56.579
Whoa, whoa!

50:57.413 --> 50:58.498
Casual.

50:58.498 --> 51:01.250
Let's hope your amigos
can keep their mouths shut.

51:01.250 --> 51:02.919
We can't blame this one
on junkies.

51:02.919 --> 51:04.837
The Cubans will never talk. Ever.

51:04.837 --> 51:07.965
Nothing leads back to us.
We're fine.

51:07.965 --> 51:09.592
Lakewood Country Club.

51:09.592 --> 51:11.260
You a member?

51:14.639 --> 51:16.390
- Bye-bye.
- All right. Let's go.

